Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:02.15,warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻譯： 雨意  天井  影子   校譯 : 影子  時間/後期 : 嵐醬  壓制: 茶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說那小鬼是受里見大人照顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有他在的地方 一定沒有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你這孩子終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都睡了一周了 也該醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 真是讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章彥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡著的時候 葬禮已經舉行過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章彥明明前一天還好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼異常…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小孩 很難判斷他到底是屬於哪個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回到這裡的時候 應該已經是那個世界的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你也要當心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一下子睡了這麼久 可能是受到了影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是信乃的寵物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它？它叫村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我沒讓它進浴池裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你居然睡了整整一周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾會昏睡不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是睡了這麼久還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服 一周沒洗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊好好洗洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃真是個不可思議的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你頭上頂著烏鴉 這也叫普通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 謝謝你找到了章彥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 信乃 我和章彥是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被神隱的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昏睡時 班級裡的女生們告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說仁可是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡特別我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在還一直活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計應該是很久以前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的真實年齡是22歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我6歲的時候在山裡失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 奶奶拜託中大師父找到我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經過了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(264,240)}陰暗的勝利感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22歲還長得這麼幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(1040,314)}根本沒在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(970,482)}漂亮助攻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺贏得太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp15\c&H000301&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(624,584)\fad(300,0)}其實是18歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說我被找到時 仍然保持6歲的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不記得發生過什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我也不怎麼在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了這裡之後 我也正常的成長起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 十年後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 信乃的身高早晚也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是防天狗的結界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都有 還真是誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說仁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他有和我們完全一樣的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他珠子的主人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那珠子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注: 日語中 珠子和蛋蛋同音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 當然是有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再確認一次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是第幾張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔 你在這裡幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次你進出這裡 結界就會被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發牢騷的時間 還不如換上強力結界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…我已經給仁更強的護符了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經回來過的孩子 還有可能再被帶走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就相傳那座山上住著天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁去那邊待得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是可憐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它喜歡這種人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的父親不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親生下他後 是瞞著村民將他幽禁起來撫養的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是16年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然找到了從懸崖跌落身亡的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從那以後 仁就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年後 我來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從它手裡救回仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把仁在那邊時的記憶封印起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它畢竟撫養仁長大 就好像父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父母的話 早晚會來把孩子帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算找到那傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 6年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是7年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明近在眼前 卻費事地找了這麼多年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你差不多也該厭倦這自在隨意的人世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵 我要找個人收養你這個拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…我…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 跟我走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 好疼啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了 什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你已經不是人類的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該早就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會來把他帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人類的孩子 把仁還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是曾經被人類拋棄過的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經是我們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回我們的孩子是父母的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 栲婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我的錫杖在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我順著氣味追過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我這次一定要滅了那只天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月 突然把這傢伙帶回來 到底想怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不是阿貓阿狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 別這麼無禮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖真乖 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不是我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子一眨眼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把一半的命給了這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他已經不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託葉月 和我一起保護這個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再讓這個孩子孤獨一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你一直這麼年幼弱小也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子很美好 孩子就應該被疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠都是孩子的摸樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月 華月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月 華月呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有覺得我們一直在剛剛的地方打轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始 好像就是山神的領域了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 這個結界能破壞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有莊介 想死你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是獵妖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那只天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遺憾的是 他不是我要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂 但是對那個孩子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許在那邊的生活才是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便告訴你個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主即將醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不可能集齊八顆明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 把珠子還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 什麼都不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再挨餓 也不必再流血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不會再讓你孤獨一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我死了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我之所以還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為華月給了我一半的命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他全心全意地在山上撫養我長大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但華月卻因我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為自從華月把一半的命給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年來 他已經用盡了作為天狗的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是華月本人所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我也不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 從那麼高的懸崖摔下來你居然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒想到會被你們救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我一生的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠我一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中大法師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還連累你受這樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是栲婆婆的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那個天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的傷痊癒後 就立刻去奪回仁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 已經對仁半放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時這一天終會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那孩子是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是什麼話啊 你不疼愛外孫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 那可是我唯一的外孫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼突然說那種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒曾經寄過一封信給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信上說「我懷了天狗的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我當時沒有相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我女兒一直活得很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想肯定是難以啟齒的對象的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒和外孫見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在女兒死後 我後悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會對那兩人置之不理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說仁真的流淌著天狗的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你想起我們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 華月死了的事也想起來了 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個沒用的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確說來 大哥並沒有真正死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬幸 華月的軀體得以保留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有一點我要說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你說想把「半身」還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月也絕不會接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的半身 將贈予這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來一切都進行得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 你以為本大爺是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 快把華月的身體還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我還什麼好處都沒拿到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣我很為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個珠子還是什麼的玩意兒 仁手上就有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搶還是要偷 隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月不在 你們也很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是仁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想見那只天狗的軀殼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你說想把「半身」還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月也絕不會接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然葉月那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻不應該接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我當時卻只是個一無所知的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華月 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是仁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的 他還只是不完全品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話 也只是個容器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的「半身」給你了吧 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你只要把得到的東西還回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你帶我回來 葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會還給華月應還之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你不要搗亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:06.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}一人にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:06.03,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}不要讓我孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甘く　甘く色をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:09.54,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甜美地 綻放色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:13.21,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:13.21,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要輕易離開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:17.59,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕の命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:17.59,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:24.47,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:24.47,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:29.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}どうして君の願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:29.77,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底是為什麼 你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:35.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみの雨に打たれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:35.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖被悲傷之雨淋透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}咲いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.86,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻依舊傲然怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:43.99,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう大事なもの傷つけたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:43.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已經不能傷害重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:48.49,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その静かな笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:48.49,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只想默默守候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:52.25,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:52.25,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你那恬靜的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:56.08,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:56.08,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}伸出你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.63,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独さえ壊すほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.63,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}去打破孤寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.76,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉の時も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.76,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到終結之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:05.64,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:05.64,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:07.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:07.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:10.72,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:10.72,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有你能照亮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:15.81,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}ただ一つの光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:15.81,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}是我唯一的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見到信乃的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為轉來了一位超可愛的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽說你實際上已經18歲時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得什麼啊根本不足畏懼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 一臉笑嘻嘻的是在找揍嗎
